<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "Eric_snowboarding.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>
          With a background in real estate investment as well as insurance, I found a passion for software engineering. This passion drives me to create applications for the benefit of society. By combining my talents, I am an asset to any company or business. Not only do I bring value, I give back to those who are needed advice in these areas in financial technology.
        </p>

        <%= render 'about_buttons' %>
        <%= render 'about_job_history' %>
        <%= render 'about_education' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>        
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
